			<p class="translateMe">Busrides is in the beta phase of development. Regular site updates are made to enhance your experience!</p>
		</div>
		<div class="beta-feedback-link cta-open">
			<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
				<path d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none" />
